        "gg5XP8u5oyz_text": "<p>Research and innovation are at the core of our mission, and our dedication to science has established the brand as a leader in the advanced skincare arena.&nbsp;<br><br>The company’s founding was the direct result of a revolutionary discovery that set the standard for antioxidant formulation. We continue to pioneer next-generation products that will optimize the health and beauty of the skin—and change the face of skincare for years to come.</p>",
