        "ggERl2la8Ci_text": "<p>\"The formula is a thick serum that sinks into the skin very quickly. There is virtually no drying-down time needed. I use this as my moisturizer, and it helps to plump and smooth my skin. It does not pill up or cause my foundation to look different.”</p>",
        "ggI9PKEl8i1_text": "<p>What A Soothing Skin Care Treatment !</p>",
